Barbara Mitchell https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Barbara_Mitchell 0 Barbara Mitchell (4 October 1929 – 9 December 1977, Kingston Upon Thames) was an English actress who became a familiar face on British television in the 1960s and 1970s, best known for her work in many classic sitcoms of the period.
